ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing and visualizing COVID-19 trends using Tableau. The goal is to transform large-scale pandemic data into interactive, insightful dashboards that support data-driven decision-making and executive-level understanding.

The analysis covers case trends, anomalies, and time-series patterns to uncover meaningful insights from complex datasets.

